In this modified version, a `HashSet` is used to store all guessed letters. Before processing a guess, the game checks if the guessed letter is in this set. If it is, the game informs the user and skips the rest of the loop iteration, asking for a new guess. If the guessed letter is not in the set, it is added to the set and the game continues as before. **Finished.**

